To: Chris at Indigo <chris@indigometrics.com>
Subject: Here's a thought:

=20

"Remote work was already a growing trend among organizations, =
particularly in Asia, says Su-Yen Wong. But there are more positive =
outcomes of remote workplaces than just allowing your teams to continue =
working when they can=E2=80=99t travel physically: The focus on =
performance and output, as opposed to just input, will also improve =
diversity, whether it=E2=80=99s better empowering working mothers or =
disabled communities, or expanding the talent pool from a recruiting =
perspective."

=20

This from a recent W50 summary I got. It's an interesting point we can =
use in promoting Indigo; that we help support diversity by focusing on =
clear indicators of performance. No?

=20

- J


